LIST

Usage: ^gLIST^n

The list command is used to list the contents of an item or shop in the
room you are currently in. 

With shops it will list all the items for sale, or that the owner can
order in for you. The price is listed along with time for the item to
come in when ordered or essence costs if cyberware.

It can also be used to list on boards and to display the status of any
programs installed in a desktop computer.
 
^WSee Also: SHOPS, BUY, SELL, VALUE, CHECK, RECEIVE, INFO^n
